textBeforeTable: iPhone 4S — 64GB model Apple yesterday announced in the US that demand for the iPhone 4S had seen 1 million devices pre-ordered in the first day alone. Carrier competitors Vodafone and Optus this week also announced prices for the iPhone 4S, with Vodafone offering the 16GB iPhone 4S with no added monthly repayment on a $59 plan over 24 months. Meanwhile, Optus offers the 16GB iPhone 4S for an additional $19 per month over 24 months.
